MINI REDIS
==========

A Redis server implemented with C++11 and Boost.

FEATURES
--------

* Fully implements the RESP2 protocol.
* Supported Redis commands:
	PING, SAVE, LOAD, SET, GET, DEL, EXPIRE, PEXPIRE, EXPIREAT, PEXPIREAT, TTL, PTTL,
	INCR, INCRBY, DECR, DECRBY

PERSISTENCE
-----------

* SAVE
	Save a snapshot to `dump.mrdb`.

* SAVE TO path
	Save a snapshot to the specified path.

* LOAD
	Load snapshot data from `dump.mrdb`.

* LOAD FROM path
	Load snapshot data from the specified path.

DEPENDENCIES
------------

* A C++ compiler supporting the C++11 standard.
* Boost Library installed on the system.

BUILD
-----

	$ cmake -B build
	$ cmake --build build

RUN
---

	$ ./build/server
